# Multiclass Classification: One-vs-all #

  _ Examples:
			_ Email foldering/tagging: Work, Friends, Family, Hobby
			_ Medical diagrams: Not ill, Cold, Flu
			_ Weather: Sunny, Cloudy, Rain, Snow

  _ if we have 3 class:

  	   _ we need 3 hypothesis: h{i}[theta](x);

